1
00:02:08,820 --> 00:02:13,100
Eternal Love of Dream

2
00:02:14,740 --> 00:02:16,620
Episode 50

3
00:02:53,340 --> 00:02:53,900
You're awake?

4
00:02:59,860 --> 00:03:00,780
Who are you?

5
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:03,300
You don't remember me?

6
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:07,660
Do you know who you are?

7
00:03:08,780 --> 00:03:10,140
I'm Bai Fengjiu from Qingqiu.

8
00:03:12,380 --> 00:03:13,220
So,

9
00:03:14,140 --> 00:03:15,300
you just forget about me.

10
00:03:19,060 --> 00:03:21,780
Take a good look at me. Who am I?

11
00:03:29,260 --> 00:03:31,460
Are you a little fox from Qingqiu?

12
00:03:36,380 --> 00:03:38,260
Are you my classmate?

13
00:03:42,620 --> 00:03:43,420
Or,

14
00:03:43,540 --> 00:03:45,980
did you have a blind date with me?

15
00:03:52,420 --> 00:03:53,220
It seems that

16
00:03:54,500 --> 00:03:55,660
you've really lost your memories.

17
00:04:01,660 --> 00:04:02,580
What a pity!

18
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:04,740
For what?

19
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:09,460
I originally planned to go to Qingqiu

20
00:04:09,700 --> 00:04:10,940
with you to meet your family

21
00:04:11,780 --> 00:04:13,420
and discuss how to hold our delayed wedding banquet

22
00:04:13,820 --> 00:04:15,380
to make you my Empress.

23
00:04:17,940 --> 00:04:19,340
Now that you've lost your memories,

24
00:04:20,620 --> 00:04:23,340
it has to be postponed indefinitely.

25
00:04:25,060 --> 00:04:25,500
What?

26
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:26,980
What?

27
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:28,180
Will you marry me?

28
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:33,900
I didn't expect that

29
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:35,980
you had forgotten it all.

30
00:04:37,540 --> 00:04:37,980
Wait!

31
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:39,340
Where are you going?

32
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:42,660
I'm going to find Lian Song

33
00:04:43,340 --> 00:04:44,740
and ask him to send you back to Qingqiu.

34
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:47,500
Then, won't you marry me?

35
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:50,380
Now that you don't remember me,

36
00:04:51,220 --> 00:04:52,460
I have to let it go.

37
00:04:53,060 --> 00:04:53,700
Actually...

38
00:04:56,540 --> 00:04:58,140
Actually, I kind of recall something.

39
00:04:59,740 --> 00:05:00,860
In the Dream of Aranya,

40
00:05:01,340 --> 00:05:02,540
we were a couple, right?

41
00:05:03,740 --> 00:05:05,780
I was Aranya, and you were Xi Ze.

42
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:09,140
What happened in the Dream of Aranya doesn't count.

43
00:05:09,820 --> 00:05:11,020
Since you can't remember me,

44
00:05:11,580 --> 00:05:13,060
don't force yourself.

45
00:05:20,380 --> 00:05:22,620
I kind of recall it.

46
00:05:23,420 --> 00:05:24,340
What do you recall?

47
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:28,300
You seem to be Emperor Dong Hua.

48
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:30,220
Seem?

49
00:05:30,340 --> 00:05:31,620
You are Emperor Dong Hua!

50
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,620
I'm Bai Fengjiu from Qingqiu.

51
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:38,740
I'm your girl, Xiaobai.

52
00:05:44,140 --> 00:05:44,740
Ouch!

53
00:05:46,860 --> 00:05:48,700
I dare not trick you next time.

54
00:05:49,220 --> 00:05:50,180
Next time?

55
00:05:50,460 --> 00:05:51,700
No. Never.

56
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:54,700
What you just said,

57
00:05:54,860 --> 00:05:55,980
does it still count?

58
00:05:58,980 --> 00:05:59,580
What did I say?

59
00:06:03,220 --> 00:06:05,180
You said you would marry me.

60
00:06:07,740 --> 00:06:10,220
Take a bath in hot spring first to recover from fatigue.

61
00:06:10,660 --> 00:06:11,780
We're leaving the valley.

62
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:13,460
I'll have Chong Lin get everything ready.

63
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:14,580
After we get out,

64
00:06:15,220 --> 00:06:15,900
I'll marry you.

65
00:06:16,180 --> 00:06:16,580
OK.

66
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:19,020
Aren't you coming?

67
00:06:22,300 --> 00:06:23,540
We haven't got married yet.

68
00:06:24,180 --> 00:06:25,500
I didn't mean that.

69
00:06:47,140 --> 00:06:48,580
The royal family of the inseparable king birds

70
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:50,180
and the royal family of the night owls

71
00:06:50,340 --> 00:06:51,460
would like to guard the valley.

72
00:06:51,980 --> 00:06:53,660
Your Majesty, please approve.

73
00:06:55,380 --> 00:06:56,020
Do you know

74
00:06:56,820 --> 00:06:58,060
what will happen to you

75
00:06:58,940 --> 00:06:59,780
if the Miaoyi Chasm is broken?

76
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:02,340
Your Majesty,

77
00:07:03,220 --> 00:07:06,220
having sealed Miao Luo for tens of thousands of years,

78
00:07:06,740 --> 00:07:09,100
the Miaoyi Chasm has been filled with her dark energy.

79
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:13,140
If Miao Luo breaks out of the seal this time,

80
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:14,820
the entire Fanyin Valley

81
00:07:15,380 --> 00:07:17,100
will be filled with dark energy.

82
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:20,340
By then, all the living things
will surely be plunged into an abyss of misery.

83
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:22,460
Wherever the dark energy reaches,

84
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:24,020
it will become barren

85
00:07:24,340 --> 00:07:25,500
and lifeless.

86
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:30,940
Are you all clear?

87
00:07:34,060 --> 00:07:35,980
Your Majesty, please approve.

88
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:38,940
We're willing to perish with the Fanyin Valley.

89
00:07:40,060 --> 00:07:40,580
Your Majesty,

90
00:07:41,300 --> 00:07:44,540
though we're not so competent as gods from the Sky Kingdom,

91
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:47,940
we're honored as royals by our clans

92
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:49,420
and have enjoyed high positions and great wealth.

93
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:51,540
If we don't stay now, we'll be too ashamed

94
00:07:52,100 --> 00:07:55,420
to see our people in future.

95
00:07:56,060 --> 00:07:57,220
Exactly!

96
00:07:57,940 --> 00:07:59,500
Though the gods from the Sky Kingdom have great magic power,

97
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:02,980
their magic power will be removed after entering the valley.

98
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:06,220
Also, the magic tricks they learned
are not as pure as those learned in the valley.

99
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:08,340
In the Fanyin Valley,

100
00:08:08,740 --> 00:08:09,860
it's nice to have some help.

101
00:08:10,740 --> 00:08:11,660
I've arranged for the clansmen

102
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:13,340
to evacuate from the valley.

103
00:08:13,780 --> 00:08:15,620
The gods from the Sky Kingdom are also ready for assistance.

104
00:08:17,580 --> 00:08:18,940
We're willing to guard the valley.

105
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:20,580
Your Majesty, please approve!

106
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:23,380
Your Majesty, please approve!

107
00:08:41,140 --> 00:08:41,980
Then please join me

108
00:08:42,780 --> 00:08:45,020
in guarding the Miaoyi Chasm.

109
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:47,580
Thank you, Your Majesty!

110
00:08:53,900 --> 00:08:56,620
This is the Lianxin Mirror
specifically used for purifying the dark energy.

111
00:08:57,220 --> 00:08:59,500
It can help you confine Miao Luo.

112
00:09:01,700 --> 00:09:02,900
Thank you, Your Majesty!

113
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:08,860
Elder brother!

114
00:09:11,340 --> 00:09:11,860
Jielu,

115
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:13,460
why are you here?

116
00:09:13,940 --> 00:09:15,260
Why do you all stay

117
00:09:15,460 --> 00:09:16,860
but me?

118
00:09:17,060 --> 00:09:18,700
I also want to stay and guard the valley with you.

119
00:09:18,820 --> 00:09:20,140
I'm also a royal.

120
00:09:20,580 --> 00:09:21,540
You're still a kid!

121
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:24,420
I go to school with you now.

122
00:09:24,620 --> 00:09:25,500
You can all stay.

123
00:09:25,540 --> 00:09:26,820
Why can't I?

124
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:29,740
Jielu,

125
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:31,420
if we all stay here,

126
00:09:32,180 --> 00:09:34,300
who can our people rely on?

127
00:09:35,300 --> 00:09:36,460
For this trip to the Sky Kingdom,

128
00:09:36,940 --> 00:09:38,100
they need someone to make decisions

129
00:09:38,260 --> 00:09:39,100
and lead them.

130
00:09:39,660 --> 00:09:41,860
Do you want our people to seek living

131
00:09:41,980 --> 00:09:43,380
in the Sky Kingdom on their own?

132
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:45,420
Can you leave instead?

133
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:46,540
Elder brother,

134
00:09:46,660 --> 00:09:48,780
you're the future king of the inseparable king birds.

135
00:09:49,060 --> 00:09:51,820
You should take our people to the Sky Kingdom,
and I'll stay here instead.

136
00:09:54,740 --> 00:09:55,740
Silly girl,

137
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:58,140
you're the only daughter of uncle and aunt.

138
00:09:59,940 --> 00:10:00,700
I promised them

139
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:02,300
to take good care of you

140
00:10:03,060 --> 00:10:04,380
and keep you safe and sound.

141
00:10:05,820 --> 00:10:06,300
Then,

142
00:10:07,780 --> 00:10:09,900
you'll all be back, right?

143
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:11,340
Well,

144
00:10:15,220 --> 00:10:16,660
we're preparing for the worst.

145
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:18,300
But with His Majesty on our side,

146
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:20,260
we won't end up like that.

147
00:10:20,580 --> 00:10:21,980
But I can't!

148
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:23,260
Elder brother,

149
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:25,220
I can't do it on my own!

150
00:10:25,860 --> 00:10:27,500
You like Her Highness Fengjiu so much.

151
00:10:27,620 --> 00:10:29,460
Are you willing to never see her again?

152
00:10:30,060 --> 00:10:31,460
I have no one to care about outside the valley.

153
00:10:31,980 --> 00:10:33,500
I grew up here as a child.

154
00:10:33,620 --> 00:10:35,060
Just let me stay.

155
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:37,780
I...

156
00:10:38,340 --> 00:10:39,740
I do like Her Highness Fengjiu.

157
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:41,820
I'll miss her in my heart.

158
00:10:42,420 --> 00:10:44,340
But I'm also the prince of the inseparable king birds.

159
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:47,340
It's my inescapable duty to guard the valley.

160
00:10:48,140 --> 00:10:48,860
I won't leave,

161
00:10:49,540 --> 00:10:50,340
and I can't leave.

162
00:10:53,220 --> 00:10:53,780
Jielu,

163
00:10:55,220 --> 00:10:56,820
we decided together that

164
00:10:57,620 --> 00:10:59,060
you should leave with our people.

165
00:11:00,140 --> 00:11:00,660
Mother,

166
00:11:01,180 --> 00:11:01,860
uncle, aunt,

167
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:02,940
and me.

168
00:11:03,180 --> 00:11:04,380
Why?

169
00:11:05,900 --> 00:11:06,420
Jielu,

170
00:11:07,180 --> 00:11:08,620
though you've never experienced the outside world,

171
00:11:09,180 --> 00:11:10,820
you've always been our hope.

172
00:11:11,420 --> 00:11:12,100
If one day,

173
00:11:12,780 --> 00:11:14,660
we are really at the critical juncture of life and death,

174
00:11:15,420 --> 00:11:16,500
as long as we know

175
00:11:16,820 --> 00:11:18,260
we've still got you to lead our people,

176
00:11:18,740 --> 00:11:19,540
we can feel relieved

177
00:11:19,660 --> 00:11:21,020
and spare no efforts in dealing with the situation.

178
00:11:21,380 --> 00:11:22,500
Elder brother!

179
00:11:25,060 --> 00:11:26,460
Mother asked me to send you a message.

180
00:11:28,620 --> 00:11:29,740
Let the tragedy of the Fanyin Valley

181
00:11:30,660 --> 00:11:32,060
stay in the Fanyin Valley.

182
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:34,900
She said you would understand it.

183
00:11:35,380 --> 00:11:37,100
But why do you have to stay?

184
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:39,420
You haven't fulfilled your wish yet!

185
00:11:40,780 --> 00:11:41,660
Mother is old.

186
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:43,540
They need me.

187
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:46,140
Moreover,

188
00:11:46,900 --> 00:11:47,500
Jielu,

189
00:11:48,620 --> 00:11:49,780
do you really have no one to care about?

190
00:11:52,260 --> 00:11:55,100
Who are you thinking of right now?

191
00:11:56,300 --> 00:11:56,900
Elder brother,

192
00:11:57,380 --> 00:11:58,540
you're making fun of me.

193
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:02,180
I still expect you to grow up and get married.

194
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:03,700
Don't panic.

195
00:12:04,540 --> 00:12:06,780
It's just a temporary separation.

196
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:08,420
Then

197
00:12:08,700 --> 00:12:10,620
you must all be safe and sound!

198
00:12:21,660 --> 00:12:23,140
I will guard this place well

199
00:12:25,180 --> 00:12:26,340
and wait for you to return.

200
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:13,660
Magnificent and unhurried,

201
00:13:15,020 --> 00:13:16,500
yet filled with deep emotions.

202
00:13:18,820 --> 00:13:19,420
Terrific!

203
00:13:21,420 --> 00:13:22,220
I was playing randomly.

204
00:13:23,100 --> 00:13:24,340
Sorry for my poor skills.

205
00:13:27,340 --> 00:13:28,540
You helped Xiaobai and me

206
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:30,020
out of righteousness this time.

207
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:32,900
I haven't thanked you yet.

208
00:13:34,020 --> 00:13:34,580
I'm so flattered.

209
00:13:36,060 --> 00:13:37,220
Your Majesty, it's the honor of a lifetime

210
00:13:37,700 --> 00:13:39,540
to be able to serve you.

211
00:13:41,060 --> 00:13:43,380
Also, you know that

212
00:13:44,900 --> 00:13:47,140
I have my selfish motive.

213
00:13:48,780 --> 00:13:50,060
That's hardly a selfish motive.

214
00:13:50,980 --> 00:13:52,620
You just want to know the truth.

215
00:13:56,300 --> 00:13:56,740
Right.

216
00:14:00,220 --> 00:14:01,300
For all these years,

217
00:14:02,940 --> 00:14:06,460
I just couldn't get over Aranya's death.

218
00:14:08,780 --> 00:14:09,740
After entering the dream world this time,

219
00:14:11,260 --> 00:14:12,100
I finally

220
00:14:13,660 --> 00:14:14,820
have taken a load off my mind.

221
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:17,180
Such a result

222
00:14:19,620 --> 00:14:21,060
may not be the one you wanted.

223
00:14:23,420 --> 00:14:24,260
To me,

224
00:14:25,820 --> 00:14:27,100
I certainly don't want to see that

225
00:14:27,780 --> 00:14:29,220
Aranya was deeply in love with Shen Ye.

226
00:14:29,940 --> 00:14:33,700
Nor do I want to believe that
Shen Ye was also deeply in love with Aranya.

227
00:14:34,620 --> 00:14:38,860
But after brooding it over here for days,

228
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:40,860
I've gradually realized that

229
00:14:43,540 --> 00:14:44,860
such a result,

230
00:14:46,180 --> 00:14:46,980
the truth,

231
00:14:49,460 --> 00:14:51,660
was actually better than I speculated.

232
00:14:56,340 --> 00:14:58,660
I feel relieved for Aranya.

233
00:14:59,820 --> 00:15:00,940
She didn't love

234
00:15:03,780 --> 00:15:06,100
the wrong guy after all.

235
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:10,980
It's rare to think like that.

236
00:15:17,740 --> 00:15:19,180
Something strange has happened inside the valley.

237
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:22,740
His Highness Lian Song didn't tell me the details,

238
00:15:24,140 --> 00:15:26,700
but I can guess a thing or two.

239
00:15:30,540 --> 00:15:31,100
Your Majesty,

240
00:15:32,260 --> 00:15:34,140
anything you ask,

241
00:15:34,900 --> 00:15:37,460
the people of West Sea will surely help you.

242
00:15:40,100 --> 00:15:41,260
It's too early to ask for help.

243
00:15:42,100 --> 00:15:43,100
I know how to deal with it.

244
00:16:09,100 --> 00:16:09,740
Jiuge,

245
00:16:10,580 --> 00:16:11,740
this is a letter from Yan to you.

246
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:12,860
Yan?

247
00:16:14,060 --> 00:16:15,540
When did he become so genteel?

248
00:16:15,660 --> 00:16:16,460
See you.

249
00:16:26,620 --> 00:16:28,580
Xiaojiu, I'm so glad that you're back!

250
00:16:29,300 --> 00:16:31,180
Can you drink wine or eat meat now?

251
00:16:31,980 --> 00:16:33,460
If you can,

252
00:16:33,820 --> 00:16:35,580
meet us in private in the Zuilixian Restaurant right away.

253
00:16:36,620 --> 00:16:38,980
Meng wants to give you a farewell dinner in private.

254
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:41,220
Since you fell into the Dream of Aranya,

255
00:16:41,660 --> 00:16:42,340
the inseparable king birds

256
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:44,420
have known that we lied about who we were.

257
00:16:45,140 --> 00:16:47,780
But due to the ice face and Lian Song,

258
00:16:48,100 --> 00:16:49,220
they dared not inquire about our true identities.

259
00:16:49,980 --> 00:16:52,100
Meng asked me in private several times.

260
00:16:53,180 --> 00:16:54,060
Given that he's a friend,

261
00:16:54,180 --> 00:16:56,300
I told him who I was honestly.

262
00:16:56,660 --> 00:16:57,940
Though I said nothing about your identity,

263
00:16:58,060 --> 00:17:00,580
he mistakenly thought that you were also a demon.

264
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:04,140
Yan was quite smart this time.

265
00:17:04,380 --> 00:17:06,140
He actually remembered to hide my identity.

266
00:17:07,420 --> 00:17:07,940
Actually,

267
00:17:08,220 --> 00:17:10,820
whom Meng loves is the legendary Fengjiu.

268
00:17:11,100 --> 00:17:12,100
It's not you.

269
00:17:12,860 --> 00:17:13,820
We're friends.

270
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:14,980
Even if he knows who you are,

271
00:17:15,340 --> 00:17:16,780
he stands no chance against the ice face.

272
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:19,220
Whether to keep hiding your identity

273
00:17:19,700 --> 00:17:20,980
or to tell him who you are,

274
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:22,340
it's up to you.

275
00:17:40,580 --> 00:17:42,220
It seems that back with four seasons,

276
00:17:42,380 --> 00:17:43,260
the Fanyin Valley is picturesque.

277
00:17:44,020 --> 00:17:46,260
It's really a reclusive land of peace and happiness.

278
00:17:47,580 --> 00:17:49,620
The Fanyin Valley was originally built outside the mortal realm.

279
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:51,700
Back then, I chose this place

280
00:17:52,060 --> 00:17:53,900
to suppress the Miaoyi Chasm

281
00:17:54,300 --> 00:17:55,580
and neutralize the dark energy in the world.

