00:30:24,820 --> 00:30:26,340
By then, you must spare no efforts.

561
00:30:26,660 --> 00:30:27,860
Just learn from Yan

562
00:30:28,300 --> 00:30:28,820
and make her love you

563
00:30:28,980 --> 00:30:30,780
as deeply as you love her.

564
00:30:31,060 --> 00:30:31,500
Do you understand?

565
00:30:31,940 --> 00:30:32,300
Yes!

566
00:30:51,220 --> 00:30:52,780
Shall we leave and give them some space?

567
00:30:54,260 --> 00:30:56,540
It's an once-in-a-lifetime opportunity for fun.

568
00:30:57,220 --> 00:30:58,860
Someone is actually trying to win over Emperor Dong Hua's woman.

569
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:01,460
How I wish I could watch closer!

570
00:31:01,860 --> 00:31:02,580
Why should I leave?

571
00:31:04,420 --> 00:31:06,700
I knew it! No one from the Sky Kingdom is good.

572
00:31:07,660 --> 00:31:08,660
You should leave actually.

573
00:31:08,860 --> 00:31:09,780
By watching them,

574
00:31:09,940 --> 00:31:11,540
I can step in if anything unpleasant happens.

575
00:31:13,460 --> 00:31:14,380
Why do you look at me like that?

576
00:31:16,260 --> 00:31:17,860
You just want to watch the drama, right?

577
00:31:19,020 --> 00:31:21,620
You're too straight-forward.

578
00:31:21,900 --> 00:31:24,100
I guessed right, didn't I? Asshole from the Sky Kingdom.

579
00:31:25,500 --> 00:31:27,100
The one you called asshole

580
00:31:27,260 --> 00:31:28,500
actually taught you how to play the game of go

581
00:31:28,860 --> 00:31:31,500
and how to win Princess Ji Heng's heart.

582
00:31:31,660 --> 00:31:33,620
Is this how you treat your master?

583
00:31:34,020 --> 00:31:34,820
What master?

584
00:31:34,980 --> 00:31:36,260
I hate playing the game of go the most.

585
00:31:36,420 --> 00:31:37,500
You're burning the bridge after crossing the river, right?

586
00:31:37,660 --> 00:31:38,140
I...

587
00:31:43,540 --> 00:31:44,020
So fast?

588
00:31:44,060 --> 00:31:44,420
Have you told her?

589
00:31:44,700 --> 00:31:45,220
Yes.

590
00:31:45,700 --> 00:31:46,540
What did Xiaojiu say?

591
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:48,820
She said we were still good friends,

592
00:31:49,260 --> 00:31:50,820
and she asked me to learn more from you.

593
00:31:51,260 --> 00:31:51,740
Learn from

594
00:31:53,060 --> 00:31:53,900
me?

595
00:31:54,460 --> 00:31:56,180
Learn from your shamelessness for sure!

596
00:32:01,420 --> 00:32:02,140
She also said that

597
00:32:02,940 --> 00:32:04,740
next time I loved someone,

598
00:32:05,420 --> 00:32:06,220
I should make her love me

599
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:08,260
as deeply as I love her.

600
00:32:14,900 --> 00:32:17,580
Then you should live up to her blessing.

601
00:32:20,020 --> 00:32:23,100
Actually, I knew it from the start.

602
00:32:25,060 --> 00:32:27,140
When I first met Her Highness Fengjiu,

603
00:32:27,900 --> 00:32:30,380
I knew she would never love me.

604
00:32:31,460 --> 00:32:32,700
She was so gorgeous,

605
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:33,700
special, charming,

606
00:32:33,860 --> 00:32:34,900
and distinguished.

607
00:32:35,340 --> 00:32:36,140
I knew it all.

608
00:32:37,740 --> 00:32:39,220
Even if I were not from the Fanyin Valley,

609
00:32:39,780 --> 00:32:41,340
even if I were from the Four Seas and Eight Deserts,

610
00:32:41,820 --> 00:32:43,100
I would still be the most unimpressive one

611
00:32:43,300 --> 00:32:44,900
among tens of thousands of people

612
00:32:45,260 --> 00:32:46,580
pursuing Her Highness Fengjiu.

613
00:32:49,700 --> 00:32:51,860
You both said that

614
00:32:52,220 --> 00:32:54,460
the woman I loved was an imaginary figure,

615
00:32:55,020 --> 00:32:56,820
not the real Fengjiu,

616
00:32:58,140 --> 00:32:58,980
but Yan,

617
00:32:59,380 --> 00:33:00,020
do you know?

618
00:33:01,580 --> 00:33:03,420
I always wanted to leave the Fanyin Valley

619
00:33:04,020 --> 00:33:04,980
not because I felt lonely in the Fanyin Valley

620
00:33:05,180 --> 00:33:07,700
for it was winter all the year round,

621
00:33:08,660 --> 00:33:09,340
but that

622
00:33:10,500 --> 00:33:11,980
I met Her Highness Fengjiu.

623
00:33:13,500 --> 00:33:14,780
I wanted to see her again.

624
00:33:15,780 --> 00:33:17,220
Even if we couldn't talk,

625
00:33:17,740 --> 00:33:18,740
it's fine.

626
00:33:20,580 --> 00:33:22,180
I started longing for the outside world

627
00:33:22,660 --> 00:33:24,540
after meeting Her Highness Fengjiu.

628
00:33:27,340 --> 00:33:28,620
To get closer to her,

629
00:33:28,780 --> 00:33:30,500
I collected all the information about her,

630
00:33:30,660 --> 00:33:31,540
even the fake one.

631
00:33:31,740 --> 00:33:32,900
As long as the information was about her,

632
00:33:33,420 --> 00:33:34,620
I just couldn't let it go.

633
00:33:36,540 --> 00:33:38,940
I knew the unrequited love wouldn't work,

634
00:33:40,220 --> 00:33:41,780
but I just couldn't give up.

635
00:33:42,100 --> 00:33:42,580
It's not because

636
00:33:43,060 --> 00:33:44,100
I'm silly,

637
00:33:44,660 --> 00:33:45,540
but that

638
00:33:46,500 --> 00:33:47,700
she's Her Highness Fengjiu.

639
00:33:48,300 --> 00:33:51,420
I had never felt the warmth of spring, summer and autumn,

640
00:33:52,100 --> 00:33:53,260
but Her Highness Fengjiu

641
00:33:53,700 --> 00:33:54,740
made me feel warm

642
00:33:55,420 --> 00:33:58,460
and made me realize the way to get warm.

643
00:34:00,260 --> 00:34:02,300
I'm really happy

644
00:34:02,580 --> 00:34:03,660
to know you

645
00:34:04,780 --> 00:34:05,980
and become good friends with you.

646
00:34:08,620 --> 00:34:10,220
I can talk to you freely and frankly,

647
00:34:11,220 --> 00:34:12,100
but when I saw Her Highness Fengjiu,

648
00:34:12,300 --> 00:34:13,740
I was speechless.

649
00:34:14,420 --> 00:34:15,820
I could only wish her the very best.

650
00:34:21,300 --> 00:34:21,900
Don't turn around.

651
00:34:24,100 --> 00:34:24,740
Don't turn around.

652
00:34:26,980 --> 00:34:28,020
You're sure to meet someone

653
00:34:28,900 --> 00:34:30,300
who matches you

654
00:34:31,100 --> 00:34:32,980
and loves you deeply.

655
00:34:34,580 --> 00:34:37,500
Now she's found her happiness.

656
00:34:38,660 --> 00:34:39,740
Stop looking at her.

657
00:34:41,100 --> 00:34:42,500
Just walk straight ahead.

658
00:34:43,620 --> 00:34:44,260
Right!

659
00:34:44,660 --> 00:34:45,260
Don't turn around.

660
00:34:45,540 --> 00:34:46,380
The road is ahead of you.

661
00:34:46,460 --> 00:34:47,460
Just go your way.

662
00:34:58,140 --> 00:34:58,820
What's this?

663
00:34:59,420 --> 00:35:01,140
I've sealed the primordial spirits of Shen Ye and Aranya

664
00:35:01,340 --> 00:35:02,620
into this tree.

665
00:35:03,860 --> 00:35:05,380
As shadows,

666
00:35:05,660 --> 00:35:07,020
they still have primordial spirits?

667
00:35:07,460 --> 00:35:07,940
Right.

668
00:35:08,780 --> 00:35:10,660
They should have vanished into the universe

669
00:35:10,860 --> 00:35:12,060
after they died,

670
00:35:12,700 --> 00:35:14,980
but if everything in the world is inferred with common sense,

671
00:35:16,180 --> 00:35:17,740
then many feelings will be wasted.

672
00:35:18,940 --> 00:35:20,220
Now that I've sealed them here,

673
00:35:20,660 --> 00:35:21,380
it's up to the will of Heaven

674
00:35:22,060 --> 00:35:25,820
whether their fates can change millions of years later.

675
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:14,740
Though they're shadows of us,

676
00:36:15,060 --> 00:36:16,820
their feelings for each other are deep and sincere.

677
00:36:17,980 --> 00:36:19,780
Your Majesty, by choosing such a good place

678
00:36:19,860 --> 00:36:20,700
to settle them down,

679
00:36:20,860 --> 00:36:23,020
you've sort of made up for their regrets when they were alive.

680
00:36:26,260 --> 00:36:27,500
We should go back now.

681
00:36:34,940 --> 00:36:35,580
Why are you smiling?

682
00:36:39,180 --> 00:36:40,660
I suddenly remembered that

683
00:36:41,380 --> 00:36:44,020
when I worked as a fairy maid in Tai Chen Palace,

684
00:36:44,700 --> 00:36:46,580
you never paid attention to me.

685
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:49,500
Now you've actually asked me to go back with you.

686
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:51,900
It feels like a dream.

687
00:36:57,340 --> 00:36:58,740
I didn't know it was you.

688
00:37:00,180 --> 00:37:02,060
What if you had known?

689
00:37:02,820 --> 00:37:03,580
If I had known,

690
00:37:05,500 --> 00:37:07,460
we wouldn't have wasted so much time.

691
00:37:32,380 --> 00:37:33,660
Ignorant youngsters,

692
00:37:35,100 --> 00:37:36,780
you actually want to confine me?

693
00:37:52,420 --> 00:37:53,340
Lianxin Mirror?

694
00:37:55,460 --> 00:37:57,820
It's actually the Lianxin Mirror
which can purify the dark energy!

695
00:37:59,260 --> 00:37:59,860
Dong Hua,

696
00:38:00,660 --> 00:38:02,380
you really gave me no chance.

697
00:38:03,460 --> 00:38:05,140
You forced me!

698
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:19,740
Nie Chuyin,

699
00:38:20,380 --> 00:38:21,180
come to me now!

700
00:38:27,180 --> 00:38:27,620
Your Majesty,

701
00:38:28,540 --> 00:38:30,100
Xu Yang has set the ward with his life.

702
00:38:30,940 --> 00:38:32,260
To enter the Forbidden Land

703
00:38:32,500 --> 00:38:33,700
and take out the blood tear now,

704
00:38:34,380 --> 00:38:35,500
Xu Yang must die.

705
00:38:36,180 --> 00:38:37,740
But with my current power,

706
00:38:38,260 --> 00:38:39,820
I can't kill Xu Yang and others all at once.

707
00:38:40,460 --> 00:38:41,540
Try everything.

708
00:38:42,100 --> 00:38:42,860
Kill him!

709
00:38:43,860 --> 00:38:44,300
Yes!

710
00:38:44,900 --> 00:38:47,100
Dong Hua has sealed part of my power.

711
00:38:47,980 --> 00:38:49,580
If I want to break out of the ward,

712
00:38:49,940 --> 00:38:51,980
I have to obtain the last blood tear.

713
00:38:52,540 --> 00:38:53,180
Take it to me

714
00:38:54,140 --> 00:38:54,820
as soon as possible.

715
00:38:55,460 --> 00:38:55,900
Yes!

716
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:33,860
What're you doing?

717
00:39:36,100 --> 00:39:36,780
Demon Lord Xu Yang,

718
00:39:37,180 --> 00:39:38,540
I just saw you reinforcing the ward.

719
00:39:39,020 --> 00:39:39,940
I was intended to help you.

720
00:39:41,900 --> 00:39:42,700
Is there anything wrong with the ward?

721
00:39:43,900 --> 00:39:45,220
I feel that something is wrong,

722
00:39:45,820 --> 00:39:48,380
but I can't figure out why.

723
00:39:49,300 --> 00:39:50,180
Let me help you reinforce the ward.

724
00:39:50,420 --> 00:39:50,780
I'll help you, too.

725
00:39:51,020 --> 00:39:51,420
Demon Lord Nie,

726
00:39:52,540 --> 00:39:54,340
please tell the other demon lords that

727
00:39:55,060 --> 00:39:56,540
the ward needs to be reinforced.

728
00:39:57,180 --> 00:39:58,660
Make sure that they come with you.

729
00:39:59,540 --> 00:39:59,980
OK.

730
00:40:18,540 --> 00:40:19,380
Xie Guchou,

731
00:40:19,740 --> 00:40:21,220
haven't you made a body for him

732
00:40:21,420 --> 00:40:22,700
with the pimpon fruit,

733
00:40:23,060 --> 00:40:24,420
why isn't he awake?

734
00:40:24,980 --> 00:40:26,380
I just finished the body three days ago.

735
00:40:26,900 --> 00:40:29,780
Moreover, buried under the imperial palace back then,
he had no bones left

736
00:40:30,140 --> 00:40:32,540
but a tiny bit of primordial spirit sealed in the Nether World.

737
00:40:33,140 --> 00:40:35,020
Unfortunately, after sleeping for a hundred years,

738
00:40:35,380 --> 00:40:37,420
his primordial spirit has fallen into quietus.

739
00:40:37,780 --> 00:40:39,820
If we resurrect him hurriedly,

740
00:40:40,060 --> 00:40:43,060
I'm afraid the dark energy
inside his primordial spirit won't be removed.

741
00:40:43,740 --> 00:40:44,740
So what?

742
00:40:46,100 --> 00:40:47,020
Even if he's awake,

743
00:40:47,460 --> 00:40:49,340
he'll be muddleheaded

744
00:40:49,700 --> 00:40:51,340
and intellectually reduced to an infant.

745
00:40:53,180 --> 00:40:53,980
What can we do

746
00:40:54,180 --> 00:40:55,540
to make him stay clear and bright?

747
00:40:56,780 --> 00:40:57,660
I do have a way,

748
00:40:58,380 --> 00:40:59,260
but...

749
00:40:59,620 --> 00:41:00,420
Please tell me.

750
00:41:03,420 --> 00:41:04,460
If an immortal

751
00:41:04,580 --> 00:41:06,420
is willing to give him half of his or her cultivation,

752
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:09,700
maybe he can remain clear and bright when he's resurrected.

753
00:41:10,140 --> 00:41:11,860
Just take my cultivation.

754
00:41:13,020 --> 00:41:14,460
Don't you want to think it over?

755
00:41:15,580 --> 00:41:17,260
Qingti sacrificed his life to save me.

756
00:41:17,540 --> 00:41:19,300
I just need to give him some cultivation.

757
00:41:19,540 --> 00:41:21,060
No need to think about that.

758
00:41:21,980 --> 00:41:23,020
One more thing.

759
00:41:23,700 --> 00:41:25,460
According to the rules of the Immortal Record Book,

760
00:41:25,820 --> 00:41:28,260
Ye Qingti has become an immortal by a rare chance,

761
00:41:28,700 --> 00:41:31,740
so the person who bestowed him with an immortal body
should go to the Ninth Heaven Jade Pool

762
00:41:31,820 --> 00:41:33,100
to help him wash away his mortal dust

763
00:41:33,500 --> 00:41:34,740
for him to become a real immortal.

764
00:41:35,300 --> 00:41:35,740
OK.

765
00:41:36,140 --> 00:41:37,700
When he wants to start his cultivation,

766
00:41:38,180 --> 00:41:38,940
I'll help him.

767
00:41:44,460 --> 00:41:45,060
Take it easy.

768
00:41:45,740 --> 00:41:46,860
The immortal body was just formed.

769
00:41:47,100 --> 00:41:47,940
Haste does not bring success.

770
00:41:49,020 --> 00:41:51,020
When the immortal body can take it,

771
00:41:51,300 --> 00:41:52,740
I'll inform you for sure.

772
00:41:53,020 --> 00:41:53,500
OK.

